Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.62,0:22:04.60,Ending English,,0000,0000,0000,,Looking at the graduation photos,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.72,0:22:09.73,Ending Romaji,,0000,0000,0000,,kimi wa me wo tojiru
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.72,0:22:09.73,Ending English,,0000,0000,0000,,You close your eyes.
