Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.87,0:22:30.64,Ending Romaji,,0000,0000,0000,,gizagiza moyou no machi no BIITO hayasugirukara
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.87,0:22:30.64,Ending English,,0000,0000,0000,,The beat to this saw-tooth patterned city is too fast,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.64,0:22:36.52,Ending Romaji,,0000,0000,0000,,SUKECCHIBUKKU mine ni kakaete tabi ni dekakeyou
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.64,0:22:36.52,Ending English,,0000,0000,0000,,So let's go out on a journey, with my sketchbook to my chest.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.52,0:22:42.33,Ending Romaji,,0000,0000,0000,,na-na-na nakushitamo mou ichido sagashite
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.52,0:22:42.33,Ending English,,0000,0000,0000,,Look for what we lost one more time,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.33,0:22:48.03,Ending Romaji,,0000,0000,0000,,na-na-na nanairo no yume wo oikakete
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.33,0:22:48.03,Ending English,,0000,0000,0000,,Chase after that seven-colored dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.12,0:22:54.03,Ending Romaji,,0000,0000,0000,,na-na-na namida iro sora ni tokashitara
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.12,0:22:54.03,Ending English,,0000,0000,0000,,If I melt the color of tears into the sky,
