Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.03,0:23:00.08,Ending English,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if a rainbow of seven colors will appear.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.01,0:23:13.81,canvas2,Elis,0000,0000,0000,,Mandarin orange is the bittersweet color of youth.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.26,0:23:17.15,canvas2,,0000,0000,0000,,But why do guys fall for childhood friends so easily?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.46,0:23:17.90,canvas2,Hiroki,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.90,0:23:21.20,canvas2,Elis,0000,0000,0000,,If you go out with someone you’ve grown up with since you were kids,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.20,0:23:22.73,canvas2,,0000,0000,0000,,you’re going to get tired of her some time!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.73,0:23:23.42,canvas2,Hiroki,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.43,0:23:27.98,canvas2,Elis,0000,0000,0000,,And when that happens, it’ll be too late to regret not expanding your view more.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.98,0:23:31.03,canvas2,Hiroki,0000,0000,0000,,But, a girl that’s similar to a sister\Nis the same thing, isn’t it?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.42,0:23:33.29,canvas2,,0000,0000,0000,,One would get tired of her even after going out.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.29,0:23:34.06,canvas2,Elis,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.42,0:23:36.50,canvas2,Kiri,0000,0000,0000,,Next episode, “Mandarin Orange Reunion”
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.50,0:23:38.61,canvas2,Elis,0000,0000,0000,,Keep romances that are outside a radius of fifty meters!
